result.execSummary:
The defendant Kolade K. Akinshemoyin was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Kolade K. Akinshemoyin is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Kolade K. Akinshemoyin was found guilty of Possession of THC (2nd+ Offense), a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).

For more information, see Wisconsin Statute 111.335 and the Department of Workforce Development's publication, Arrest and Conviction Records under the Law.
